    <title>博客个性化-二维码展示</title>
    <link href="https://cocosongying.github.io/hexo/p/f78c.html"/>
    <id>https://cocosongying.github.io/hexo/p/f78c.html</id>
    <published>2019-05-05T12:00:07.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-05T12:20:35.585Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>改造 Hexo 主题 <a href="https://xaoxuu.com/wiki/material-x/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Material X</a> 侧边栏添加二维码展示，用于将当前页的 URL 地址生成二维码，方便移动终端扫码直接访问。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>在主题文件夹下新建文件 layout/_widget/qrcode.ejs</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;section class=&apos;widget &lt;%- item.widget?item.widget:&apos;qrcode&apos; %&gt;&apos;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;%- partial(&apos;header&apos;, &#123;item: item, defIcon: &apos;&apos;, defTitle: &apos;&apos;&#125;) %&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;div class=&apos;content &lt;%= theme.style %&gt;&apos;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;canvas id=&quot;qrcode&quot; src=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;width:100%; display:flex; justify-content:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;/canvas&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;script type=&quot;text/javascript&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">      var url = window.location.href;</span><br><span class="line">      var c=document.getElementById(&quot;qrcode&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">      var ctx=c.getContext(&quot;2d&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">      var qr=new Image();</span><br><span class="line">      qr.src=&apos;&lt;%- qrcode(url) %&gt;&apos;;</span><br><span class="line">      qr.onload = function() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        ctx.drawImage(qr,100,0,100,100);</span><br><span class="line">      &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">  &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/section&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成QRcode需要安装插件：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm i -S hexo-helper-qrcode</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>配置文件中添加侧边栏配置</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sidebar:</span><br><span class="line">  - widget: qrcode</span><br><span class="line">    icon: fas fa-qrcode</span><br><span class="line">    title: 扫一扫手机浏览</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h2><p>查看本文侧边栏二维码生成结果</p>]]></content>
    
