  <entry>
    <title>博客个性化-打赏按钮</title>
    <link href="https://cocosongying.github.io/hexo/p/3821.html"/>
    <id>https://cocosongying.github.io/hexo/p/3821.html</id>
    <published>2019-05-05T10:55:53.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-05-05T11:32:38.710Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在博客页添加一个打赏按钮，点击打赏，弹出赞赏码，扫描赞赏码对博主进行打赏鼓励。</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><p>html 代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;! -- 添加捐赠图标 --&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;div class =&quot;post-donate&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div id=&quot;donate_board&quot; class=&quot;donate_bar center&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;p style=&quot;margin:5px auto;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot; onclick=&quot;document.getElementById(&apos;donateModal&apos;).style.display = &apos;block&apos;&quot; style=&quot;display:block;width:100px;padding:10px;background-color:#E74851;color:#fff;text-align:center;margin:0px auto;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;transition: all 0.3s;&quot;&gt;打赏&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;br/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;div id=&quot;donateModal&quot; class=&quot;modal&quot; style=&quot;display: none;position: fixed;z-index: 1000;margin-left:-160px;margin-top:-200px;padding: 10px;left: 50%;top: 50%;width: 320px;height: 380px;overflow: auto;background-color: rgb(0,0,0);background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.6);&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;img src=&quot;https://cocosongying.github.io/img/wechatpay.jpeg&quot; id=&quot;myImg&quot; width=&quot;298&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; style=&quot;border:1px solid #d3d3d3;margin-bottom: 12px;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        &lt;p style=&quot;margin:5px auto;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;javascript:void(0)&quot; onclick=&quot;document.getElementById(&apos;donateModal&apos;).style.display=&apos;none&apos;&quot; style=&quot;display:block;width:100px;padding:10px;background-color:#E74851;color:#fff;text-align:center;margin:0px auto;text-decoration:none;border-radius:10px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;transition: all 0.3s;&quot;&gt;关闭&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;! -- 添加捐赠图标 --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>css 代码</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">.donate_bar &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  text-align: center;</span><br><span class="line">  margin-top: 5%</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">.donate_bar .donate_txt &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  display: block;</span><br><span class="line">  color: #9d9d9d;</span><br><span class="line">  font: 14px/2 &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#donate_guide&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  height: 250px;</span><br><span class="line">  width: 250px;</span><br><span class="line">  margin: 0 auto;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#donate_guide img&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  height: 240px;</span><br><span class="line">  height: 240px;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="赞赏码"><a href="#赞赏码" class="headerlink" title="赞赏码"></a>赞赏码</h2><p>如何获取赞赏码？</p><p>微信可通过 支付 –&gt; 收付款 –&gt; 赞赏码 按照步骤开通并保存</p><p>支付宝可通过 收钱 –&gt; 保存图片 直接得到收钱码</p><h2 id="示例"><a href="#示例" class="headerlink" title="示例"></a>示例</h2><p>查看本文下方的赞赏码</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;在博客页添加一个打赏按钮，点击打赏，弹出赞赏码，扫描赞赏码对博主进行打赏鼓励。&lt;/p&gt;
    
